something on my own.

504
00:25:58,641 --> 00:25:59,766
That's why I lied to you.

505
00:25:59,850 --> 00:26:01,726
If I call your office
tomorrow and I check...

506
00:26:01,810 --> 00:26:03,895
Call my office,
call my secretary,

507
00:26:03,979 --> 00:26:06,105
call my clients,
interrupt their dinner,

508
00:26:06,190 --> 00:26:07,357
wake them up, I don't care.

509
00:26:07,441 --> 00:26:09,484
I just want you
to know the truth.

510
00:26:11,654 --> 00:26:13,488
You know I love you.

511
00:26:15,908 --> 00:26:17,283
Come here.

512
00:26:18,369 --> 00:26:19,619
Please.

513
00:26:27,544 --> 00:26:28,920
