535
00:27:23,517 --> 00:27:24,976
Think what you want.

536
00:27:25,060 --> 00:27:26,811
By the way,
your orderly's outside.

537
00:27:26,895 --> 00:27:29,564
But I'd wait about
another 10 minutes

538
00:27:29,648 --> 00:27:30,857
if you really want
your husband to think

539
00:27:30,941 --> 00:27:33,568
you're having
radiation treatments.

540
00:27:36,071 --> 00:27:37,447
Dr. Hadley?

541
00:27:38,407 --> 00:27:40,533
Are you, by chance, gonna cry?

542
00:27:41,410 --> 00:27:44,120
'Cause that's the one
I just can't do.

543
00:28:02,389 --> 00:28:05,099
Hello? This is Dr. Hadley.

544
00:28:09,438 --> 00:28:10,563
What?

545
00:28:14,568 --> 00:28:16,361
You called the medical board?

546
00:28:16,445 --> 00:28:17,487
