551
00:28:24,453 --> 00:28:27,497
Dr. Hadley, get out here now.

552
00:28:37,299 --> 00:28:38,420
You're acting like an idiot.

553
00:28:38,467 --> 00:28:40,343
She's trying to make me
lose my license!

554
00:28:40,427 --> 00:28:42,053
She'll fail, unless
you're stupid enough

555
00:28:42,137 --> 00:28:43,262
