and scream at her.

556
00:28:43,347 --> 00:28:45,473
Sexual harassment accusations
are incredibly serious.

557
00:28:45,557 --> 00:28:47,809
If she made them anonymously,
the case goes away.

558
00:28:47,893 --> 00:28:51,229
If she used her name, we all
back you up, it goes away.

559
00:28:51,313 --> 00:28:52,814
You're completely overreacting.

560
00:28:52,898 --> 00:28:55,024
You'd be pissed off, too,
if you were me.

561
00:28:55,109 --> 00:28:56,190
Or maybe not, I don't know.

562
00:28:56,193 --> 00:28:57,794
You're just about as
emotional as she is.

563
00:28:57,820 --> 00:28:59,237
I'm doing you a favor. I know.

564
00:28:59,321 --> 00:29:03,408
And even when you try to do something
nice, you sound like a jerk.

565
00:29:04,660 --> 00:29:06,035
I'm sorry.

566
00:29:07,788 --> 00:29:09,122
For what?

567
00:29:10,582 --> 00:29:12,291
For firing you.

568
00:29:12,501 --> 00:29:14,221
Don't do that. That's
not what this is about.

569
00:29:14,253 --> 00:29:16,504
Then I'll apologize anyway.

570
00:29:16,588 --> 00:29:18,881
I did it for me, not for you.

571
00:29:20,467 --> 00:29:23,219
